metadata.name: Dark Machine #1
metadata.description:
The Dark Machines are 8888 unique Gen 1 avatars. There are 171 assets paired with 6 traits, randomly generated on the blockchain. The permutations are endless, resulting in limitless possibilities ranked by their rarity. Each and every detail has been painstakingly hand illustrated by our talented artists.

Immerse yourself in Sora's Dreamworld to unravel what lies ahead in this superlunary world with our Sandbox metaverse construction in progress.
